dotfiles for osx

Currently using the following:

* terminal is osx default Terminal
* Terminal theme is Material shell
* Font is MesloLGS NG Regular Font 12 pt
* shell is zsh `.zshrc`
* shell plugins managed with antibody (~/.zsh_plugins.txt)
* shell prompt is powerlevel10k
* vim colorscheme is apprentice
* npm packages are globally installed per `.npmrc`
* eslint config uses airbnb style guide
